METAVERSE

1. Definition
The Metaverse is a virtual, shared, and immersive digital space where users interact with each other and digital objects using avatars.
Access via VR, AR, PCs, and smartphones
Combines social interaction, gaming, economy, and creativity

2. Key Features
Persistent World: Exists continuously, even when users are offline
Interactivity: Socialize, work, play, trade, create
Immersion: 3D spaces, VR/AR experiences, real-time interaction
Economy: Virtual assets, NFTs, digital land

3. Applications / Use Cases
